abstract: The sacred books of the Buddhists are perfectly appalling in their bulk. They are called the Tripitaka, the Three Baskets, and were originally written in Pali, a vernacular form of Sanskrit. abstract: AMHERST, Mass., Nov. 2. -- Amherst beat Williams to-day by a score of 16 to 4 in the first game of the series for the championship of the triangular league. The weather was the worst for football ever seen in Amherst. Sleet began to fall about noon, and at 3 P.M. it settled down into a heavy snow storm. The bad condition of the field prevented any long runs. Both teams played without their Captains.

abstract: CINCINNATI, Nov. 26. -- A terrific windstorm swept over this section last night, doing considerable damage to property. Trees were uprooted buildings unroofed or wrecked, telegraph poles and wires blown down, and several boats in the river were torn from their moorings, and set adrift. abstract: BUFFALO, Nov. 26. -- One of the most furious windstorms of recent years raged to-day over the eastern portion of Lake Erie.
